        <summary>How far in advance should I book?</summary>
        <p>We require 30 days advance booking to ensure quality and availability.</p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you deliver nationwide?</summary>
        <p>Yes! We serve Lagos, Abuja, Port Harcourt, and other major cities.</p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Can I customize the menu?</summary>
        <p>Absolutely! We work with your preferences and dietary needs.</p>
    </details>
    
